subject: Beach Volleyball
lead_paragraph: The Olympic gold medalists Misty May-Treanor and Kerri Walsh lost for the second time since the Beijing Games and missed their first tour final since April 2007, falling to Jen Boss and April Ross, 21-18, 15-21, 20-18, in the semifinals of the AVP Crocs Cup Shootout in Santa Barbara, Calif.
